1
00:15:02,777 --> 00:15:04,779
May the All Mother...

2
00:15:04,987 --> 00:15:07,031
...smile upon our first meeting.

3
00:15:07,198 --> 00:15:10,368
Not bad. You sound a little formal.

4
00:15:11,619 --> 00:15:13,704
I studied for five years...

5
00:15:13,871 --> 00:15:16,040
...but there is much to learn.

6
00:48:35,579 --> 00:48:38,415
Calm, people. Calm.

7
00:48:44,171 --> 00:48:46,966
What are you doing, Tsu'tey?

8
00:48:49,468 --> 00:48:52,429
These demons are forbidden here.

9
00:48:53,180 --> 00:48:55,349
There has been a sign.

10
00:48:55,516 --> 00:48:57,851
This is a matter for the Tsahik.

11
00:49:02,690 --> 00:49:03,649
Bring him.

12
00:50:26,899 --> 00:50:28,192
Father...

13
00:50:29,068 --> 00:50:30,861
...I see you.

14
00:50:42,581 --> 00:50:44,041
This creature...

15
00:50:44,291 --> 00:50:47,419
...why do you bring him here?

16
00:50:48,837 --> 00:50:50,214
I was going to kill him...

17
00:50:50,506 --> 00:50:52,341
...but there was a sign from Eywa.

18
00:50:52,508 --> 00:50:54,426
I have said...

19
00:50:54,593 --> 00:50:56,512
...no dreamwalker will come here.

20
00:50:58,722 --> 00:51:01,058
His alien smell fills my nose.

21
00:51:13,195 --> 00:51:14,655
Step back!

22
00:51:16,990 --> 00:51:20,202
I will look at this alien.

23
00:52:17,968 --> 00:52:19,052
A warrior!

24
00:52:19,261 --> 00:52:20,596
I could kill him easily!

25
00:52:20,846 --> 00:52:22,097
No!

26
00:52:22,556 --> 00:52:26,602
This is the first warrior dream walker...

27
00:52:26,769 --> 00:52:28,562
...we have seen.

28
00:52:28,729 --> 00:52:31,607
We need to learn more about him.

29
00:52:34,026 --> 00:52:35,819
My Daughter...

30
00:52:35,986 --> 00:52:40,199
...you will teach him our way...

31
00:52:40,365 --> 00:52:43,660
...to speak and walk as we do.

32
00:52:43,827 --> 00:52:47,456
Why me? That's not fair...

33
01:00:25,038 --> 01:00:27,165
This alien will learn nothing...

34
01:00:27,624 --> 01:00:29,250
...A rock sees more...

35
01:00:29,626 --> 01:00:31,503
...look at him.

36
01:10:01,155 --> 01:10:02,490
Look how big you are.

37
01:10:04,659 --> 01:10:06,369
You are so pretty.

38
01:15:26,939 --> 01:15:28,190
I see you...

39
01:15:28,899 --> 01:15:29,900
...Brother

40
01:15:29,984 --> 01:15:32,069
...and thank you.

41
01:15:36,198 --> 01:15:37,741
Your spirit goes with Eywa.

42
01:15:38,492 --> 01:15:40,536
Your body stays behind...

43
01:15:40,619 --> 01:15:43,497
...to become part of The People.

44
01:20:53,890 --> 01:20:55,809
That moron's going to die.

45
01:21:19,666 --> 01:21:21,418
Don't be afraid, warrior.

46
01:33:25,183 --> 01:33:29,437
You are now a son of the Omaticaya.

47
01:33:30,688 --> 01:33:33,858
You are part of The People.

48
01:41:20,741 --> 01:41:22,868
Tsu'tey will lead the war party.

49
01:41:29,500 --> 01:41:30,751
Stop, Please!

50
01:41:32,253 --> 01:41:34,338
This will only make it worse.

51
01:41:37,383 --> 01:41:39,093
We will strike them in the heart.

52
01:42:56,629 --> 01:42:58,464
I have something to say...

53
01:43:00,799 --> 01:43:02,301
...to all of you.

54
01:43:37,795 --> 01:43:39,171
You see?

55
01:43:39,380 --> 01:43:41,840
It is a demon in a false body.

56
01:50:05,265 --> 01:50:06,266
Father!

57
01:50:06,558 --> 01:50:07,434
Mother!

58
01:50:07,601 --> 01:50:10,687
Eytukan, I have something to say.

59
01:50:10,937 --> 01:50:12,272
Listen!

60
01:50:13,398 --> 01:50:14,858
Speak, Jakesully.

61
01:50:16,234 --> 01:50:19,112
A great evil is upon us...

62
01:50:19,529 --> 01:50:21,406
The Sky People are coming...

63
01:50:21,656 --> 01:50:24,159
...to destroy Hometree.

64
01:51:39,484 --> 01:51:40,569
Bind them.

65
01:51:42,279 --> 01:51:43,363
Leave now!

66
01:52:40,587 --> 01:52:44,257
Have no fear.

67
01:53:05,070 --> 01:53:06,446
Take the ikran...

68
01:53:06,613 --> 01:53:08,156
...attack from above.

69
01:54:42,375 --> 01:54:44,044
Get everyone to the forest.

70
01:59:30,747 --> 01:59:31,748
Father!

71
01:59:47,680 --> 01:59:48,890
Daughter...

72
01:59:50,183 --> 01:59:53,227
take...my...bow.

73
01:59:57,398 --> 02:00:01,819
Protect The People.

74
02:11:46,065 --> 02:11:48,317
Tsu'tey, son of Ateyo...

75
02:11:48,984 --> 02:11:51,028
...I stand before you...

76
02:11:52,029 --> 02:11:55,157
...ready to serve the Omaticaya people.

77
02:13:51,190 --> 02:13:53,775
Hear us please, All Mother.

78
02:13:54,359 --> 02:13:56,653
Eywa, help her.

79
02:13:57,362 --> 02:13:59,531
Take this spirit into you...

80
02:14:03,118 --> 02:14:05,704
...and breathe her back to us.

81
02:14:09,124 --> 02:14:10,792
Let her walk among us...

82
02:14:13,295 --> 02:14:15,255
...as one of The People.

